orpor with the costs of decreased immune competence. Interbout arousals allow\nhibernators to optimize these, and other, trade-offs during prolonged hibernation by enabling\nhost responses to pathogens within brief, periodic episodes of euthermy.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Field, Kenneth Alan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sewall, Brent J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Prokkola, Jenni M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Turner, Gregory G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gagnon, Marianne F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lilley, Thomas M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "White, J. Paul", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Johnson, Joseph S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hauer, Christopher L", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Reeder, DeeAnn M.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Pathogenesis", "hibernation", "thermoregulatory behavior", "transcriptomics", "white nose syndrome", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/eda4fd09c85e778fcab719965dbe4ecc", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/ab01dfaa34026aa1e7e75a914d4c98ac739071d3554e80ee2e4428e40a4f0714", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/C4FMJ39V", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/C4FMJ39V", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/5f90255940936d49df82b5add3049f2a!/b28756-31681", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"